            <name>Statement_Text</name>
            <fieldText>&lt;p&gt;&lt;b style=&quot;font-size: 18px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);&quot;&gt;Statement of Confidentiality&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 16px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102);&quot;&gt;I understand that during and after an assignment:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;ol&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 16px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102);&quot;&gt;I will keep secret and confidential all information made available to me about my customer, any member of staff or the business of the client(s) I have been assigned to.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 16px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102);&quot;&gt;I will keep all such information secure and will not disclose it nor allow it to be disclosed to any unauthorised person.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 16px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102);&quot;&gt;Upon completion or end of my assignment, I will return all property, ID, paperwork and any associated items to a representative of yours or the client&apos;s representative.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 16px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102);&quot;&gt;I understand that the above undertakings are terms of my assignment and should I break any of them, this may result in action, not excluding Civil or Criminal Prosecution being taken against me.&amp;nbsp;This includes the Data Protection Act 1998 and any variations that may be made to this in the future.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ol&gt;</fieldText>
